  <brief_title>Quantitative Sensory Testing of the Lower Lip After Inferior Alveolar Nerve Block, and Evaluation of the Role of the Contra-lateral Inferior Alveolar Nerve</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
