  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the contribution of the innervation of the
      contra-lateral mandibular nerve for the innervation of the lower lip area.

      The investigators hypothesis is that the sensation of the lower lip is contributed by both
      mandibular nerves (from both sides of the jaw).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
